AI-Powered Incident Summarization

Many SOCs waste time on writing long incident notes. Using XSOAR’s integration with LLM/AI (OpenAI, Azure OpenAI, etc.), incidents can be summarized automatically.

### Flow (ASCII Diagram)

+--------------------------+
| Incident Created (SIEM)  |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Automation Trigger       |
| (on new incident)        |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Collect Evidence         |
| (logs, alerts, emails)   |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| AI Summarization         |
| (OpenAI / Azure OpenAI)  |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Add Summary to War Room  |
| + Notify Analyst (Slack) |
+--------------------------+

**Benefit:** analysts get a quick readable summary in <30s, saving 10–15 min per ticket.
